    "longBusinessSummary": "Ho Chi Minh City Securities Corporation, a securities brokerage firm, provides financial products and services to private, institutional, corporate clients in Vietnam. The company offers account management; consulting and order placing; brokerage; security custody; margin lending; OTC book management; bondholder agent and management; covered warrant; derivatives brokerage; active bonds; ETF funds; and auction services. It also provides institutional brokerage; corporate access; treasury services; and research services. In addition, the company provides equity capital market services, such as equitization, IPO advisory, listing, and private placement advisory services; debt capital market services, including bond issuance and loans arrangement; and merger and acquisition; corporate finance advisory services. Ho Chi Minh City Securities Corporation was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
